{"tid":1020673,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"曖昧對象話自己A2 但他fd話係A6 算唔算濫？","createTime":"2019-02-13T18:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T23:26:00.000Z","uid":200590,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d5c04c612b200f333964c7459d96c9580f35f4c9","tid":1020673,"uid":200590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:17:11.000Z","msg":"如題 定其實正常？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n在這快餐愛情世界 好像有不少A380<br />\n係咪個個報細數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d8e109484433148c2ea01acbe14d67346028fa","tid":1020673,"uid":41139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"可能佢fd講笑姐 想造尻佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb3c80f9b619e5849675f8f4dc6a74c75a666c9","tid":1020673,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:20:16.000Z","msg":"我都以為佢愛我，<br />\n原來自己一廂情願<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec6293762f9d4e554028d48a5246df6beda7dbd","tid":1020673,"uid":95499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:20:46.000Z","msg":"搞咗4次基冇話你知啫"},{"pid":"cdc20c25d18f505d4f95acae2383bc0bdff0a016","tid":1020673,"uid":5151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:22:19.000Z","msg":"拍拖多就代表濫？仲以為係得兒登青頭仲活係80年代"},{"pid":"ed974779a2aaa59334145ced9858c8f4998df075","tid":1020673,"uid":10277,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:23:25.000Z","msg":"假設你曖昧對象是男性<br />\n<br />\n他自稱A2（第一手資料）<br />\n他朋友稱他為A6（第二手資料）<br />\n<br />\n假設曖昧對象曾經與4名女性交往<br />\n其後與2名男性交往<br />\n<br />\n我們可得出算式：<br />\n<br />\n1+1+1+1-1-1=2<br />\n<br />\n結論曖昧對象是A2"},{"pid":"cbcfd60b8a5dae33f1bb9323a82a228fd79b384e","tid":1020673,"uid":137847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T18:25:04.000Z","msg":"一個係認真 一個係散拖"},{"pid":"b6d21db8384d71854b67096c2cb3caa11c5d2bdd","tid":1020673,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T23:26:00.000Z","msg":"每個人計嘅方法都唔同<br />\n有啲人要認真先計<br />\n有啲人散拖都計<br />\n甚至有人係連未正式開始就完咗嘅曖昧都計<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}